    {
      "segment_id": "cf898102",
      "source_content": "This document describes how to start Chaos Mesh quickly in a test or local environment.",
      "source_content_hash": "9226c304cf8a9eeaf594094b054bffba8c4840dff287a013402a5231deef1107",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "本文件說明如何在測試或本地環境中快速啟動 Chaos Mesh。"
      },
      "invalid_translations": {}
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "a7378c68",
      "source_content": ":::caution\n\n**In this document, Chaos Mesh is installed via a script for quick trial only.**\n\nIf you need to install Chaos Mesh in the production environment or other strict non-test scenarios, it is recommended to use [Helm](https://helm.sh/). For more details, refer to [Installation using Helm](production-installation-using-helm.md).\n\n:::",
      "source_content_hash": "82547a63c04f84317cf02826f85aa9532f8626227d3e3595319fe4b3ce3f269a",
      "node_type": "containerDirective",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": ":::caution\n\n**本文件僅描述透過腳本快速試用 Chaos Mesh 的安裝方式。**\n\n若需在生產環境或其他嚴格的非測試情境下安裝 Chaos Mesh，建議使用 [Helm](https://helm.sh/)。更多詳細資訊，請參閱 [使用 Helm 安裝](production-installation-using-helm.md)。\n\n:::"
      },
      "invalid_translations": {}
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "ed7dde9c",
      "source_content": "## Environment preparation",
      "source_content_hash": "e5f5bb1c4a07acdb4d72895ce64eb75416847741ef4095e5a8d4b201a92302a4",
      "node_type": "heading",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "## 環境準備"
      },
      "invalid_translations": {}
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "a76548f8",
      "source_content": "Please ensure that the Kubernetes cluster is deployed in the environment before the trial. If the Kubernetes cluster has not been deployed, you can refer to the links below to complete the deployment:",
      "source_content_hash": "1bd84b390f27fd53cf7b215776ab3db2c9d6546c77e16e1397ec99e0ed649d27",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "在試用前，請確保環境中已部署 Kubernetes 叢集。若尚未部署 Kubernetes 叢集，可參考以下連結完成部署："
      },
      "invalid_translations": {}
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "2523feeb",
      "source_content": "- [Kubernetes](https://kubernetes.io/docs/setup/)",
      "source_content_hash": "f52cc59a84fd1098aafa419b6730acd852706b58d32ec95cd3ff592f177fd6be",
      "node_type": "listItem",
      "translatable": true,
