      },
      "invalid_translations": {}
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "97ae4a01",
      "source_content": "To install Chaos Mesh in a test environment, run the following script:",
      "source_content_hash": "da3d074f9677d6be1447a1f5c234040e71c8460d437595bb3d99a7e4a4aea99e",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "若要在測試環境中安裝 Chaos Mesh，請執行以下腳本："
      },
      "invalid_translations": {}
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "28e10980",
      "source_content": "<!-- prettier-ignore -->",
      "source_content_hash": "a94eeea12154992988ea88567eed85506a35d1f83e439a912e23fafd65191f47",
      "node_type": "comment",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_28e10980"
      },
      "invalid_translations": {}
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "1641af73",
      "source_content": "<Tabs defaultValue=\"k8s\" values={[\n  {label: 'K8s', value: 'k8s'},\n  {label: 'kind', value: 'kind'},\n  {label: 'K3s', value: 'k3s'},\n  {label: 'MicroK8s', value: 'microk8s'}\n]}>\n  <TabItem value=\"k8s\">\n    <PickVersion>\n    {`curl -sSL https://mirrors.chaos-mesh.org/latest/install.sh | bash`}\n    </PickVersion>\n  </TabItem>\n  <TabItem value=\"kind\">\n    <PickVersion>{`curl -sSL https://mirrors.chaos-mesh.org/latest/install.sh | bash -s -- --local kind`}</PickVersion>\n\n    If you want to specify a `kind` version, add the `--kind-version xx` parameter at the end of the script, for example:\n\n    <PickVersion>\n    {`curl -sSL https://mirrors.chaos-mesh.org/latest/install.sh | bash -s -- --local kind --kind-version v0.20.0`}\n    </PickVersion>\n\n  </TabItem>\n  <TabItem value=\"k3s\">\n    <PickVersion>\n    {`curl -sSL https://mirrors.chaos-mesh.org/latest/install.sh | bash -s -- --k3s`}\n    </PickVersion>\n  </TabItem>\n  <TabItem value=\"microk8s\">\n    <PickVersion>\n    {`curl -sSL https://mirrors.chaos-mesh.org/latest/install.sh | bash -s -- --microk8s`}\n    </PickVersion>\n  </TabItem>\n</Tabs>",
      "source_content_hash": "a31240841302552e4c581fc59c94a2267947f295458c1b56ccd0427912f1ce73",
      "node_type": "mdxJsxFlowElement",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_1641af73"
      },
      "invalid_translations": {}
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "eab056be",
      "source_content": "After running, Chaos Mesh will automatically install the appropriate version of CustomResourceDefinitions and the required components.",
      "source_content_hash": "a75493b5fca3be279060f69bf535a40307e44eac5d662dffa8985f153b7977db",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "執行後，Chaos Mesh 會自動安裝適當版本的 CustomResourceDefinitions 和必要元件。"
      },
      "invalid_translations": {}
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "f01228d3",
      "source_content": "For more installation details, refer to the source code of the [`install.sh`](https://github.com/chaos-mesh/chaos-mesh/blob/master/install.sh).",
      "source_content_hash": "0fb34d07f57fc65db37c19611d09e7ec714acbe7f9d780f67bb0bb4fcea11ace",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "更多安裝細節，請參考 [`install.sh`](https://github.com/chaos-mesh/chaos-mesh/blob/master/install.sh) 的原始碼。"
