      "segment_id": "0a103a02",
      "source_content": "## Uninstall Chaos Mesh",
      "source_content_hash": "ab80d8b7494f870b8fc95c1724720f1abc9e343d7de90d1758433f83418c2bb6",
      "node_type": "heading",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "## 解除安裝 Chaos Mesh"
      },
      "invalid_translations": {}
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "8126f763",
      "source_content": "To uninstall Chaos Mesh, execute the following command:",
      "source_content_hash": "5f34dc8c1d90d6968703a678bcd3e0b49211ebb9cc10fd684eac3df252a3378f",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "若要解除安裝 Chaos Mesh，請執行以下命令："
      },
      "invalid_translations": {}
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "897e0025",
      "source_content": "<PickVersion>\n{`curl -sSL https://mirrors.chaos-mesh.org/latest/install.sh | bash -s -- --template | kubectl delete -f -`}\n</PickVersion>",
      "source_content_hash": "2195cc2c39d6c9727be14dc1db90159566fe50de9ee32e5cf091f8fda2c4ac99",
      "node_type": "mdxJsxFlowElement",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_897e0025"
      },
      "invalid_translations": {}
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "51867d16",
      "source_content": "You can also delete the `chaos-mesh` namespace to directly uninstall Chaos Mesh:",
      "source_content_hash": "dbe2860d9c2714a5b356c1bbde0c045bad3433ce6059a68df01a310da1e68113",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "您也可以刪除 `chaos-mesh` 命名空間來直接解除安裝 Chaos Mesh："
      },
      "invalid_translations": {}
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "59f28e14",
      "source_content": "```sh\nkubectl delete ns chaos-mesh\n```",
      "source_content_hash": "a8b21828d0291a7daff067d83ee2183b78a33d8c62c2148940c967ea6e9b60c4",
      "node_type": "code",
      "translatable": false,
